title: Housefull 2
subTitle: Four men join hands to date and marry the women of their dreams by changing their identities and deceiving their prospective fathers-in-law.

title: Tejaa
subTitle: Tejaa's family gets murdered when he is a child. Later, in an attempt to seek revenge, he traces down the three goons who were responsible.

title: Takkar
subTitle: Ravi Malhotra, a photographer, is framed by a corrupt policeman, D'Costa, on the day before his wedding. While in jail, Ravi studies law to exact revenge against his perpetrator.

title: Pyar Ke Do Pal
subTitle: Twins Sunil and Anil try to reunite their parents who separated many years ago due to a tragic misunderstanding regarding a friend's wish to have an abortion.

title: Suhagan
subTitle: Janki's life changes when she leaves her obsolete married life and runs away with Murli. However, trouble ensues when Murli commits suicide.

title: Main Hoon Na
subTitle: Major Ram is given orders to go undercover as a college student to protect a general's daughter from a rogue soldier. He must also fulfil his dying father's desire to reconcile with his family.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.

title: Itihaas
subTitle: Naina, who is betrothed to an influential man, falls in love and elopes with Karan, the son of an employee of her fiance. Soon, bounty hunters start hunting the duo to claim a hefty reward.

title: Yodha
subTitle: Karan, a lawyer, and Suraj, a victim of fate, find themselves fighting for the same cause when they take on the anti-social elements to rid the society of its ills.

title: Deewana Tere Naam Ka
subTitle: Friends Shankar and Shambhu share a lot in common and also end up falling in love with the same girl. However, when the girl loves Shankar, Shambhu parts ways with him and joins his rival.

title: Jurmana
subTitle: A flambouyant businessman places a bet with his former college friend to woo their professor's young daughter. However, the bet leads to a series of unexpected consequences.

title: Aladin
subTitle: Aladin, an orphan tormented by bullies, discovers a magic lamp that grants him incredible powers. Later, with the help of a genie, he embarks on thrilling adventures to defeat the evil Ringmaster.

title: Dushmani
subTitle: Suraj and Sapna, lovers belonging to enemy families, find their relationship threatened by bullets and betrayal when their brothers collide.

title: Gumrah
subTitle: Seeing Roshni's talent for singing, Rahul gives her a break and they eventually fall in love. On a foreign trip, she is arrested for possession of cocaine, not knowing that it is all Rahul's doing.

title: Bumm Bumm Bole
subTitle: An idealist elder brother lands in a dilemma after he misplaces his little sister's shoes. Unable to afford a new pair, the siblings agree to share the shoes, leading to several escapades.

title: Student of the Year 2
subTitle: Rohan follows his lover, Mridula, to St Teresa's college hoping to reunite with her. There, he befriends Manav, the most popular student, but is constantly at loggerheads with his sister, Shreya.

title: Phir Hera Pheri
subTitle: The lives of Raju, Shyam and Baburao change completely when they get cheated by a fraudster.Desperate to repay a loan from a feared gangster, they scramble to find an alternative solution.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Gupt

title: D-Day
subTitle: Intelligence officer Wali Khan and a team of highly-trained officers are set to nab Goldman, one of India's most wanted terrorists. However, their mission is threatened by a minor miscalculation.

title: Hera Pheri
subTitle: Vijay and Ajay make a living by stealing money from people. Their friendship is affected when Vijay discovers that Ajay's father may have been his father's killer.

title: Zameer
subTitle: A young man claims to be a horse-breeder's long-lost son, but all is not as it seems when he falls in love with the horse-breeder's daughter.

title: Ek Hi Raasta
subTitle: Army officer Vikram works with terrorist Kubla and steals vital army information for him. In the process, he ends up killing a colleague and pins the blame on a fellow soldier.

title: Talaash: The Hunt Begins
subTitle: Arjun grows up to be a high-profile vigilante after his father's murder and sister's abduction. Soon, he vows revenge and sets out on a mission to find his sister.

title: Darr
subTitle: Swept up in a whirlwind of fear and romance, Kiran teeters on the edge of a mental and emotional precipice. While Sunil keeps holding on to her, Rahul spares no effort to drag her down with himself.

title: Hungama
subTitle: A millionaire businessman living in a village decides to move to the city with his wife. However, things take a comical turn as a case of mistaken identity causes chaos in their lives.

title: Elaan
subTitle: A.C.P. Ramakant Chaudhary, an uptight police officer, struggles with bringing his elder son's killers to justice. Vishal, his younger son, decides to take matters in his own hands.
